🐍 A simple snake game designed using pygame in python

🟩 The snake is green 
🟤 The food is brown

⌨️ Use either "WASD" or arrow keys to navigate


// CURRENT IMPROVEMENTS //
- snake must stay within border
- if snake runs into itself, game is over
- snake grows with every snack
- snake does not go bakc into itself

// THINGS TO IMPROVE //
- show high score
- if input entered too quickly, it will ignore second input
